{"tid":258489,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"柯潔斥央視英文台記者：「若你是支那人就用支那話問我」，但不穿漢服捉圍棋","createTime":"2017-05-26T07:16:42.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-26T11:12:29.000Z","uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"335be58920cd227eb27a4213ebe32001356a3335","tid":258489,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-26T07:16:43.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=5QliDTjJa8Q&amp;feature=share\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D5QliDTjJa8Q%26feature%3Dshare&d=dYncJl1cW2%2B2jV20k7EwDu9M5Ue6CDmcYDZznX2R1Ws%3D&h=62212af6\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=5QliDTjJa8Q&amp;feature=share</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://nanchong.scol.com.cn/sdtp/img/attachement/jpg/site110/20140909/50e549817af11578a60d0a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnanchong.scol.com.cn%2Fsdtp%2Fimg%2Fattachement%2Fjpg%2Fsite110%2F20140909%2F50e549817af11578a60d0a.jpg&h=e5decd80&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n5月25日，柯潔二戰AlphaGo再次落敗。在賽後新聞發布會上，柯潔表示輸給AlphaGo有些遺憾，曾認為自己離勝利很接近。而後，支那國際電視台（CGTN，央視旗下的國際電視網）記者用流暢英文向柯潔提問，遭柯潔質疑：「如果你是支那人的話，就應該用支那話向我提問題。」現場旋即響起掌聲和歡呼聲。<br />\n<br />\n當晚，CGTN官方微博發道歉信，向柯潔「求原諒」。<br />\n<br />\n該記者立即解釋了英文提問是工作需要，並用支那話重複了一遍問題，柯潔才回答：「AlphaGo認為我下得還不錯，我覺得這也是對我最大的肯定。我當時太激動，真的太緊張，所以沒下好。非常感謝有AlphaGo這麼強大的對手，今天的棋對我也是最大鼓勵。」"},{"pid":"6d0f898318a4c847cd231f29930e9adb89ba889f","tid":258489,"uid":55533,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-26T07:18:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 條柒頭柒夠未"},{"pid":"d46548485c304bfda8632322e1866a1ad3e23d67","tid":258489,"uid":44298,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-26T07:21:44.000Z","msg":"個記者會淨係請支那傳媒未可以講支那話囉"},{"pid":"89a4f04a30b15ff1533e6b874a98be1e9aeaf118","tid":258489,"uid":1818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-26T07:23:12.000Z","msg":"下面有留言話個支那記者發音柒<br />\n<img src=\